headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ on Auto Shop Client Jobs and Exotic Exports
content:
It’s important to maintain a legitimate front. Take your Auto Shop for example: don’t get so caught up taking down The Union Depository that you forget to check in on new Auto Shop Deliveries and Exotic Exports.

Both are paying out double the usual GTA$, so make sure to shift the right vehicles from A to B in as pristine a condition as possible.
